0.4.0 (2018-10-29)
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

- Adds agencies and memberships.
  [msom]

- Enables polymorphic subclasses of people.
  [msom]

- Adds content and meta columns to people.
  [msom]

- Requires Python 3.6.
  [href]

- Refactors the package.
  [msom]

